 drivers/net/wireless/ath/wil6210/wil6210.h  |  3 ++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/wil6210/wmi.c      | 76 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/wil6210/wmi.h      | 33 +++++++++++++
